    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@shakefu The current SearchBox state is that we are now using icons by default for search and reset buttons. So there's no more \"translations\",  if you want to have a reset text button in latest version you can do this: https://jsfiddle.net/6p0ta8op/1/\r\n\r\nWe might want to revisit the SearchBox component if we have another good complete proposal allowing both text and icons in an easy way where styling is also easily.",
